<p>
  <span class="nym">Bonaventure</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>bonaventura</i> 'good luck'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of an important 13th C Franciscan scholar and saint.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


